Sacha Grunpeter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sacha_Grunpeter 0 Sacha Grunpeter was a British actor best known for his portrayal of Michael in Agony Again and Didier Baptiste in Dream Team. Shortly before his death, he also co-wrote, produced and portrayed a character in the film Tracing Cowboys.
